_json.gridTitle: Easy Old Fashioned English Sticky Gingerbread Loaf Recipe  - Food.com
_json.description: Just the smell of this gingerbread loaf whilst its baking is redolent of when I was a little girl and staying at my grandparents old cottage..........and, it is so easy to make. Plus, there are not many ingredients to it and yet, it is the recipe I always turn to when I feel like real old-fashioned sticky gingerbread! My grandmother used to serve it in thick slices with butter; it nearly always appeared on the tea table at least once a week! This is also wonderful served up as a Pudding type cak
